The paper discusses the emerging research field of dataset search or retrieval, which involves frameworks, methods, and tools to match user data needs against a collection of datasets. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well as natural language processing (cs.CL) and deep learning (cs.DL) which are used in related areas such as entity-centric and tabular search. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
